longBusinessSummary: Dlaboratory Sweden AB (publ) an energy technology company, provides inspection services solutions for owners and operators of power, telecom, and rail infrastructure in Sweden. The comoany provides dLab platform that offers bulk of the work by collecting and analysing data with timely alerts, analysis, and other KPIs. Dlaboratory Sweden AB (publ) was founded in 2007 and is headquartered in Lund, Sweden.
